    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just being overwhelmed though. it feels deeper. like there's a piece of my soul that's just gone after everything i've been through. i've tried the \"small steps\" and the \"support\" before. it doesn't change the fact that i'm just... damaged goods. it's like trying to fix a machine that's been crushed. it's just not possible to make it whole again.",
