    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's just what people say to feel better about themselves. the reality is that some things can't be \"repaired\" or \"reimagined.\" i look in the mirror and i don't see someone who needs a specialist, i just see someone who is done. it's like the engine is gone. there's no point in trying to keep a car running if the core part is melted down, you know? it just's not meant to go any further.",
